title: Microsoft Money 2005 UK
description:
Money Standard 2005 automatically consolidates all your online financial information in one place and provides fast, complete answers to your basic financial questions. Its automated features, like getting account balances and transactions from your bank and auto-categorization of spending, help simplify your life by showing you how much you have and how much you&#039;re spending. Money makes it easy to keep tabs on areas that matter to you, like dining out and groceries.
